  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\"\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\" \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd. \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffna in the \"Police Force\" case. Dismissal of the Municipal Chief Minister",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna City Chief Minister V. Manivannan has been acquitted from the case related to the \"Police Force\" created by the Jaffna City Council and the court has also ordered that the uniforms of the police force be returned.",
        "In April 2021, the police force was created by the Jaffna Municipal Council.",
        "Jaffna. The police force was formed to carry out the activities of improving city hygiene, imposing punishment against those who throw garbage in public places, spitting in public places, and subjecting them to legal action if necessary.",
        "The anti-terrorist unit conducted investigations as the uniform of the said police force was similar to the uniform of the LTTE police.",
        "Earlier, the anti-terrorist unit, which had started investigations with the members of the police force, followed by Jaffna Municipal Council member V. Investigations were also conducted against Parthipan.",
        "Subsequently, the anti-terrorist unit called Jaffna Municipal Council Chief Counsel V. Manivannan for questioning at the Jaffna Police Station, arrested the Chief Minister and took him to Vavuniya for further investigations.",
        "The day after the investigations, the Chief Minister was released on bail by the court after the Jaffna Magistrate produced the Chief Minister.",
        "In this case, when the said case was taken up today on Wednesday, Jaffna after the Attorney General's Department announced to the court that the case was not pursued further. The petition acquitted the mayor from the case and ordered the police uniforms which had been submitted as evidence to be handed over to the municipal council.",
        "The re-establishment of the police force formed with the aim of improving sanitation in the areas under the jurisdiction of the Jaffna Municipal Council was prosecuted for falsely claiming that the uniform of the LTTE was similar to that of the police.",
        "Municipal council member V. Partheepan said."
      ],
